## Lane warm-up manifest (R&D dispatch)

Normative field semantics: [`.sedea/centers/sedea/docs/lane-manifest-contract.md`](.sedea/centers/sedea/docs/lane-manifest-contract.md). R&D authoring notes: [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/docs/development-process.md`](../docs/development-process.md) § *Lane warm-up manifest contract*. Spawn/reload bindings: [`.sedea/centers/sedea/rules/4_mission.mdc`](.sedea/centers/sedea/rules/4_mission.mdc) § *Lane warm-up manifest (spawn and reload)*.

```text
effectiveWarmUp = dedupe( sedeaBootstrapRules → rdBootstrapRules → laneRules → skillWarmUp )
```

| Layer | Owner | Content |
|-------|--------|---------|
| **Sedea `bootstrapRules`** | Host | **`.sedea/centers/sedea/rules/bootstrap.mdc`** (≤ ~15 KB) |
| **R&D `bootstrapRules`** | Host when `centerSlug === research-and-development` | **This file** — `.sedea/centers/research-and-development/rules/bootstrap.mdc` (≤ ~10 KB) |
| **`laneRules`** | Mission protocol / spawn request / lane record | Role-specific governance beyond both bootstrap layers |
| **`skillWarmUp`** | Skill frontmatter + run-request **`warmUpRules`** | Subject to **384 KiB** combined warm-up cap |

Definitive per-role **`laneRules`** minimums: [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/README.md`](../missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/README.md) § *Definitive `laneRules`*. Skill **`SKILL.md`** § *Warm-up manifest* tables document **`skillWarmUp`** and **`laneRules`**; **`bootstrapRules`** rows document the R&D bootstrap path for host parity lint.

**Spawned children:** Assigned **`SKILL.md`**, validated **`inputs`**, merged **`warmUpRules`**, and persisted spawn handover define the lane contract after reload — not center READMEs alone.

